SELECT * FROM cat_complete_cast_1 AS cc,    cat_comp_cast_type_1 AS cct1,    cat_comp_cast_type_1 AS cct2,    cat_company_name_1 AS cn,    cat_company_type_1 AS ct,    cat_keyword_1 AS k,    cat_movie_companies_1 AS mc,    cat_movie_info_1 AS mi,    cat_movie_keyword_1 AS mk,    cat_title_1 AS t WHERE t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.keyword_id = k.id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.company_type_id = ct.id AND mc.company_id = cn.id AND mi.movie_id = t.id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND cct1.kind IN ('cast', 'cast', 'cast', 'cast', 'cast') AND cct2.kind = 'complete+verified' AND cn.country_code != '[az]' AND (cn.name LIKE '%Company%' OR cn.name LIKE '%Argentina%') AND ct.kind = 'distributors' AND k.keyword = 'female-nudity' AND mc.note IS NULL AND mi.info IN ('PFM:35 mm', 'PFM:35 mm', 'PFM:35 mm', 'PFM:35 mm', 'PFM:35 mm') AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1990 AND 2001 LIMIT 5;
